PN,42901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,FA mother from Northumberland says she
OL,7,Fhas been forced to turn off her boiler
OL,8,Fand use a log burner instead to keep
OL,9,Fher family warm due to the recent
OL,10,Fincrease in the cost of heating oil.
OL,12,FRachel Douglas relies on an oil boiler
OL,13,Fto heat her home in Seahouses, which
OL,14,Fis not connected to the mains gas
OL,15,Fnetwork.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
