OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,FShe refills her tank about once a year
OL,7,Fand said she has seen the price of
OL,8,Fheating oil more than double in the
OL,9,Flast two weeks. While 1,000 litres
OL,10,Fpreviously cost her around #500, she
OL,11,Fsaid it is now #700 for 500 litres.
OL,13,FOil prices have soared since the US
OL,14,Fand Israel began strikes on Iran,
OL,15,Freaching near four-year-highs above
OL,16,F100 US dollars per barrel on Monday,
OL,17,Fbefore falling to 91 dollars a barrel
OL,18,Fon Tuesday as Donald Trump said the
OL,19,Fwar could soon be over.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,FDomestic heating oil is used to warm
OL,7,Faround 1.5 million UK homes with
OL,8,Fapproximately 5% seeing its prices
OL,9,Frise dramatically amid the crisis in
OL,10,Fthe Middle East.
OL,12,FRachel told ITV Tyne Tees that
OL,13,Falthough she can afford to fill up her
OL,14,Ftank under the new prices, she feels
OL,15,Ffor others who cannot. She said:
OL,16,F"Those who are in fuel poverty, it
OL,17,Fmust be dreadful for them. I really
OL,18,Ffeel sorry for them, and for the
OL,19,Fpeople who have no choice but to pay
OL,20,Fthe extortionate prices for the
OL,21,Fheating oil.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,F"We've got a lot of holiday lets, a
OL,7,Flot of elderly residents who have to
OL,8,Fpay those prices and it will put
OL,9,Fpeople into real fuel poverty."
OL,11,FSimon Bainbridge, a farmer in Morpeth,
OL,12,Fsays he is completely reliant on
OL,13,Fheating oil and is concerned the knock-
OL,14,Fon effect this will have on consumers.
OL,16,F"It is a worry," he said. "I just kind
OL,17,Fof look at my farm as my own little
OL,18,Feconomic community, and I just try and
OL,19,Flook after us and the team.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,F"In the grand scheme of things, it's
OL,7,Fnot really worth worrying about,
OL,8,Fbecause am I going to be able to
OL,9,Fchange it?"
OL,11,FCampaigners who want to end fuel
OL,12,Fpoverty say anyone affected should
OL,13,Fseek support from Citizens Advice, but
OL,14,Fthey say if this crisis continues, the
OL,15,Fgovernment will soon need to step in.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,FMatt Copeland, from National Energy
OL,7,FAction, said: "This could have quite a
OL,8,Fsignificant impact, depending on the
OL,9,Flength of the issue. If this is
OL,10,Fprolonged, the Government will need to
OL,11,Fprovide support to people; initially
OL,12,Fto people who are reliant on heating
OL,13,Foil to be able to afford to heat their
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,F"If this bleeds through for a long
OL,17,Ftime and increases gas and electricity
OL,18,Fprices that people pay at home we
OL,19,Fmight need to revisit how we support
OL,20,Fpeople."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
