OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773765957
OL,3,CNorthumberland woman refusing to pay
OL,4,Cfuel prices as costs double
OL,6,FSpeaking in the House of Commons
OL,7,Ftoday, Chancellor Rachel Reeves said
OL,8,Fshe recognises the "unique issues
OL,9,Faround heating oil". Ms Reeves has
OL,10,Fasked the Competition and Markets
OL,11,FAuthority (CMA) to look at the cost of
OL,12,Fheating oil, as well as fuel pump
OL,13,Fprices, to prevent price gouging.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
